title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses Aaron Judge tying Roger Maris with his 61st homer of the season last night. Blue Jays Bullpen Catcher Matt Buschmann caught the ball. He and his wife Sara Walsh, who works for the NFL Network joined us. And Former NFL QB Drew Brees previews tonight's Thursday Night Football game between the Bengals and the Dolphins

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
